name: Senior #26 - Karen
description:
Karen is a 60-year-old spa manager who rarely accomplished any work, or anything in general. She is obsessed with diet coke, spray tanning, and returning Amazon packages for maximum refunds. She likes to think she eats healthy, her favorite food is cobb salad with extra ranch.

She is very confident and brave, but can also be extremely aggressive, inappropriate and batshit crazy.

She has one daughter with husband Bruce: Brailynn, aged 15.
